Happy new year and merry Christmas! 🎄

Happy monstera Monday with that beast from Costa Rica! Anyone ever wanted/thought to move to a warmer country? Where you can grow these plants in your garden... 🌿🤗
Via: @kim_sevenseas

Happy #monsteramonday 💚 This lovely lady is beyond ready to be moved to a bigger pot. I’ve been putting it off since winter, but I can’t put it off any longer. Please tell me I’m not the only one who procrastinates in repotting certain plants. 🙊#monstera #variegatedmonstera via: @foreverplanty

The final form ⭐️
.
.
This leaf might very well be my favourite - almost half half, lots of fenestrations, pure white and perfect shape☺️. What’s more exciting is that a new leaf is already on the way!
.
.
I have had the greenhouse for about a month and a half now and I am really getting used to managing it based on the weather forecast- I know when to open the roof vents, I know when to turn on heater, I have figured out the watering frequency and I have installed a fan to prevent stagnant air.
.
.
For those interested in the details:
• Temp: average 28 during the day, 21 at night
• Humidity: average of 85%
• Light: really bright indirect - polycarbonate panels and 70% shadecloth combine to prevent burning
.
.
I feel well prepped for winter and im hoping I can maintain decent growth despite the cool change...
.
.
Have a great week everyone - whatever happened last week doesn’t have to define this one ☀️
.
.
Plant ID: Variegated Monstera Deliciosa var. Borsigiana

“Size does matter. The heavyweights monstera Thai constellation in Bandung, West Java - Indonesia. Picture taken by me with my plant sisters, we purposely visit this site to see this magnificent beauty”

Says and shows: @sabrinashinta 🌿

Flaunting in the gardening scene for almost 3rd year now and I believe certain plant always have a special place in our heart. And for me, it’s this variegated banana (musa ae ae) that got me falling for it... crazily searching for it... and if you love them enough, they thrive for you! Now, it’s either #lovemeorleafmebaby 😘

Text & photo: @lovemeorleafmebaby Thank you 💚
